name: Captivating Crossroads
oracle_text:

As Captivating Crossroads enters, choose a color.
{T}: Add one mana of the chosen color.

oracle_text:
Flash

name: Jewel Mine Overseer
oracle_text:
When Jewel Mine Overseer enters, conjure seven cards named Seven Dwarves on top of your library. They perpetually gain "When this creature enters, draw a card." Then shuffle.
At the beginning of your upkeep, exile the top card of your library. You may play that card this turn.

name: Hex, Kellan's Companion
oracle_text:
Haste
Whenever you cast an Adventure spell, if Hex, Kellan's Companion is on the battlefield or in exile, it perpetually gets +1/+1. Then if it's on the battlefield, exile it with a fetch counter on it.
Whenever you cast a spell from exile, if Hex is in exile with a fetch counter on it, put it onto the battlefield.

name: The Conundrum of Bowls
oracle_text:
(As this Saga enters and after your draw step add a lore counter. Sacrifice after III.)
I — Seek a card with mana value less than the number of cards in your hand.
II — Seek a card with mana value greater than the number of cards in your hand.
III — Count the number of cards in your hand. You may cast a spell with mana value equal to that number from your hand without paying its mana cost.

name: Paths of Tuinvale
oracle_text:
Choose one or both —
• Return target creature you control to its owner's hand. That card perpetually gains "This spell costs {1} less to cast."
• Return target creature you don't control to its owner's hand. That card perpetually gains "This spell costs {1} more to cast."

name: Grow Old Together
oracle_text: Seek two creature cards from among the top ten cards of your library, then shuffle. Creature cards in your hand perpetually get +1/+1.

name: Swine Rebellion
oracle_text: If you control three or more Boars with different names, conjure each card from the Three Pigs spellbook onto the battlefield. If you control two or fewer Boars with different names, conjure two cards of your choice from the Three Pigs spellbook into your hand, then put one of them onto the battlefield.

name: Syr Joshua and Syr Saxon
oracle_text:
Double team

oracle_text:
